thread.title: BRIEF-Kayne Anderson Energy Total Return Fund Enters Into $75 Mln Revolving Credit Facility

title: BRIEF-Kayne Anderson Energy Total Return Fund Enters Into $75 Mln Revolving Credit Facility
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - Kayne Anderson Energy Total Return Fund Inc:
* KAYNE ANDERSON ENERGY TOTAL RETURN FUND ENTERS INTO $75 MILLION REVOLVING CREDIT FACILITY
* KAYNE ANDERSON ENERGY TOTAL RETURN FUND INC - ‍ CREDIT FACILITY HAS A 364-DAY TERM, MATURING ON FEBRUARY 15, 2019​
* KAYNE ANDERSON ENERGY TOTAL RETURN FUND -‍ FACILITY REPLACES $75 MILLION UNSECURED REVOLVING CREDIT FACILITY THAT WAS SCHEDULED TO MATURE ON FEB 28, 2018​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
